1. uŋ₃-e udu-gin₇ u₂ ka-ba mu-ni-ib-<<ni>>-[gu₇]
#lem: uŋ[people]; udu[sheep]; u[plant(s)]; kag[mouth]; gu[eat]
#etcsl: line-id=1

2. ud re-a {d}ezina₂ še gu nu-[zu]
#lem: ud[sun]; re[that]; Ezina[1]DN; še[barley]; gu[cord]; zu[know]
#etcsl: line-id=2

3. an-ne₂ an-šag₄-ta im-da-an-ed₃-de₃
#lem: An[1]DN; anšag[the interior of heaven]; ed[go up]
#etcsl: line-id=3

4. {d}en-lil₂-le a₂!(DA) tarah-gin₇ hur-saŋ galam X-da ed₃-de₃ igi mi-ni-ib-il₂-il₂-i
#lem: Enlil[1]DN; a[arm]; durah[wild goat]; hursaŋ[mountain]; galam[skilful]; X; ed[go up]; igi[eye]; il[raise]
#etcsl: line-id=4

5. igi-ni sig-še₃ mu-un-il₂ a-ab-ba sug₄-ga-am₃
#lem: igi[eye]; sig[weak]; il[raise]; aʾabak[sea]; sug[full]
#etcsl: line-id=5

6. igi-nim-še₃ mu-un-il₂ kur šim {ŋiš}erin-na-kam
#lem: iginim[upper land]; il[raise]; kur[mountain(s)]; šim[aromatic substance]; eren[cedar]
#etcsl: line-id=6

7. {d}en-lil₂-le še in-dub# kur-re ba-an-šum₂
#lem: Enlil[1]DN; še[barley]; dub[heap up]; kur[mountain(s)]; šum[give]
#etcsl: line-id=7

8. he₂-ŋal₂ kalam-ma-ke₄ in-X kur in-nu-ha# X im-ma#-an-šum₂#
#lem: heŋal[plenty]; kalam[the Land (of Sumer)]; X; kur[mountain(s)]; in.nu.HA[type of barley]; X; šum[give]
#etcsl: line-id=8

9. hur-saŋ ŋal₂ da₁₃-da₁₃# igi ba-ni-in-tab-tab
#lem: hursaŋ[mountain]; ŋal[open]; taka[set aside]; igi[eye]; tab[double]
#etcsl: line-id=9

