24. a-na-gin₇-nam kur-še₃ i₃-sub₂-be₂-en-de₃#-[en]
#lem: anagin[how?]; kur[mountain(s)]; sub[imperfect plural stem of ŋen⟦to go⟧]
#etcsl: line-id=24

25. še kur-ba a-na#-gin₇-nam# im-ta-ab#-ed₃-de₃-en-de₃#-[en]
